title: Ep 35: Success and Failure
description: In this episode my beloved, Tom Segura and I discuss what makes people successful and what seems to lead to failure. In all the books written about success, there seems to be a prevailing formula on how to get it. Bunz and I get deep on what these formulas are. Get your success jeans on, bros!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
